query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 10 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('amazon-s3',
'async-await',
'clojure',
'concurrency',
'configuration',
'database-design',
'error-handling',
'file-io',
'flask',
'hash',
'indexing',
'ipad',
'npm',
'null',
'orm');
